import React from "react"
import ReactDOM from "react-dom"
import KanbanBoard from "./MyComponent"
import { StreamlitProvider, withStreamlitConnection } from "streamlit-component-lib"

const WrappedKanbanBoard = withStreamlitConnection(KanbanBoard)

ReactDOM.render(
  <React.StrictMode>
    <StreamlitProvider>
      <WrappedKanbanBoard />
    </StreamlitProvider>
  </React.StrictMode>,
  document.getElementById("root")
)
